# Band Landing Page

Responsive landing page created as a frontend test assignment.

## Live Demo

[View the live website](https://mr-pavlo.github.io/band-landing-page/)

## Screenshot

Тут пізніше можна додати скриншот сторінки.

## Technologies

- HTML5
- SCSS
- Flexbox
- Responsive Web Design
- GitHub Pages

## Features

- Semantic HTML structure
- Responsive layout
- Mobile-friendly navigation
- Reusable SCSS variables and mixins
- Hover effects and transitions

## About the Project

The page was created independently from a provided reference
as part of a frontend test assignment.

